## HDD MOUNT----

create a hdd folder in standrad user

1. Mkdir Hdd
2. vi /etc/fstab
3. /dev/sda1	 /home/users/user-name/hdd 	ext4 	 defaults 	 0 0
3. mount -a


## Up swap memory---
1. sudo fallocate -l 12G /swapfile
2. ls -ll/swapfile
enable swapfile-
make the file only accessible to root-

3. sudo chmod 600/swapfile
4. ls -ll/swapfile 
5. sudo mkswap /swapfile

making swapfile permanent-
6. mount -a 
and swapon/swapfile
7. echo '/swapfile none swap sw 0 0 '|sudo tee -a/etc/fstab   




















